    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300114085_7_2259-2327",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "2259-2327",
      "markText": "人一走，留在家乡的童年和少年就像合上的书。往昔美好的故事、亲切的人物、甜醉的情景，就像鲜活的花瓣夹在书页里，再翻开都变成了干枯了的回忆。",
      "totalCount": 629,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300114085&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2259&rangeEnd=2327",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8a132890813ab9310g0154b4?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2259&rangeEnd=2327"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300114085_10_4220-4272",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "4220-4272",
      "markText": "人间的情感无须营造，存在的方式各不相同。灼热的激发未必能够持久，疏淡的方式往往使醇厚的内涵更加意味无穷。",
      "totalCount": 570,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300114085&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=4220&rangeEnd=4272",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8a132890813ab9310g0154b4?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=4220&rangeEnd=4272"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300114085_8_2136-2163",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "2136-2163",
      "markText": "是不是每个人都有这样一双眼睛，就看我们能不能把它点亮。",
      "totalCount": 507,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300114085&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2136&rangeEnd=2163",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8a132890813ab9310g0154b4?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2136&rangeEnd=2163"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300114085_22_3241-3331",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "3241-3331",
      "markText": "我要留住这一天。人生有些日子是要设法留住的。因为在这种日子里，总是在失去很多东西的同时，得到更多的——关键是我们是否能够看到。如果看到了它，就会被它更正对人生的看法并因之受益一生。",
      "totalCount": 432,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300114085&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=3241&rangeEnd=3331",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8a132890813ab9310g0154b4?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=3241&rangeEnd=3331"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300114085_6_7638-7675",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "7638-7675",
      "markText": "这事一直像个谜存在我心里，直到我入了社会，经事多了，才解开这积存已久的谜。",
